Feature List

☐ Conditional fields (branching logic)
☐ Multiple page forms
☐ Repeatable fields (one-to-many answers)
☐ Calculated fields
☑ File upload
☐ Input validation
☐ Spam protection with filters and captchas
    Via captha input field with validation
☐ Option to Save progress and resume a response later
    $form->saveProgress();
☐ Option to Preview a response before submitting it
    $form->preview();
☐ Form and field templates
☐ Built-in protection against cross-site scripting and SQL injection attacks
☐ Web standard compliance
☐ Supports over 30 languages and international character sets
